 HERE is one of the major trends you shouldn’t be seen without this season: black and white. The combo has suddenly become must-have fashion item. In the last few months, black and white fashion has gradually found its way back, and it’s more daring and stylish than it used to be. These days, it is not uncommon to see celebrities splashing lively and attractive monochrome (black and white) designs in sheer slinky fabrics, ruffle, lace trimming and slips. They are versatile pieces and, can be dressed up or down depending on the occasion. So, are you looking for a dress that is trending  one that would stay in your wardrobe for much longer? Then, the black and white fashion is your best bet. Check out our favourite celebs for  monochrome style inspiration. 